					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Mega Man X2 sets the Cx4 configuration differently than Mega Man X3. I don't recall the details. It's related to ROM configuration. I think X2 might use two MaskROMs. To use just one, you'd probably need to alter the ROM image to set the register for a single ROM chip.</div>

